item.title: CVE-2018-3661|2024-08-05T04:50:30.374Z -- intel%20corporation -- system%20configuration%20utilities
item.description: Buffer overflow in Intel system Configuration utilities selview.exe and syscfg.exe before version 14 build 11 allows a local user to crash these services potentially resulting in a denial of service.
